```sh
$ npm uninstall dtrace-provider
```

```sh
$ cd myblog
$ npm install
```

[](https://gist.github.com/btfak/18938572f5df000ebe06fbd1872e4e39)

```sh
$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save
```

_config.ymlgit

```yml
# Deployment
## Docs: http://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html
deploy:
	type: git
	repo: git@github.com:slavikshen/slavikshen.github.io.git
	branch: master
```

## 

```sh
hexo deploy
```

Post.title: HexoVSCode
Post._content:
## 

VSCodeHexo

## NPM Package



```json
"scripts": {
	"deploy": "hexo clean && hexo deploy;",
	"hot-server": "hexo server & hexo generate --watch"
}
```

deploy

```sh
$ npm run deploy 
```

hot-server

```sh
$ npm run hot-server
```

## VSCode Task

```json
{
	// See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=733558
	// for the documentation about the tasks.json format
	"version": "0.1.0",
	"command": "npm",
	"isShellCommand": true,
	"showOutput": "always",
	"suppressTaskName": true,
	"tasks": [
		{
			// 
			"taskName": "deploy",
			"args": ["run", "deploy"]
		},
		{
			// 
			"taskName": "test",
			"args": ["run", "hot-server"]
		}
	]
}
```

## 

VSCode <kbd>CMD/CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>SHIFT</kbd>+<kbd></kbd>test

Output

```sh
> hexo-site@0.0.0 hot-server /Users/slavik/Documents/myblog
> hexo server & hexo generate --watch

INFO	Start processing

```
